      "paragraphs": [
        {
          "id": "para-0-0",
          "content": "OpenAI has announced the global rollout of group chats in ChatGPT, expanding the feature to all users on Free, Go, Plus, and Pro plans following a successful pilot in select Asia-Pacific markets. The announcement was made on Thursday, November 20, 2025, just one week after the feature began testing in regions including Japan, New Zealand, South Korea, and Taiwan. This launch represents a significant shift in how the AI assistant functions, transforming it from a one-on-one tool into a collaborative platform where multiple participants can engage in shared conversations.",
