        {
          "id": "para-0-1",
          "content": "The group chat feature allows up to 20 people to participate in a single conversation thread, with ChatGPT available to assist, analyze, or respond when needed. Users can create or join group chats by tapping a people-shaped icon and either adding participants directly or sharing an invitation link. The feature is designed for various collaborative activities, including planning trips, co-writing documents, settling debates, and conducting research together. When users join or create their first group chat, they are asked to set up a profile with their name, username, and photo to ensure everyone knows who is participating in the conversation.",
