                  "name": "venturebeat",
                  "url": "https://venturebeat.com/ai/chatgpt-group-privacy/",
                  "favicon": "https://www.google.com/s2/favicons?domain=venturebeat.com&sz=32"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "para-1-1",
          "content": "OpenAI has designed the AI to be context-aware within group settings, intelligently knowing when to participate and when to stay quiet during natural group discussions. ChatGPT will only respond when directly tagged by users, preventing interruptions and allowing the AI to remain appropriately silent during human-to-human exchanges. The assistant can also react to messages with emojis and reference profile photos to enhance the conversational experience and feel more natural within group conversations.",
