    {
      "id": "section-2",
      "title": "Enterprise and Future Outlook",
      "paragraphs": [
        {
          "id": "para-2-0",
          "content": "The early feedback from the group chat pilot has been positive, prompting OpenAI to accelerate the global rollout timeline. Industry observers see potential applications across multiple sectors, from casual use cases like friends deciding on restaurant recommendations to professional applications such as team brainstorming, document collaboration, and project planning. The feature's flexibility in supporting group-specific instructions for tone, personality, and conversation style suggests that businesses and marketing teams may leverage group chats for client collaboration and creative workflows.",
